---
import { pageTitle, SITE_EMAIL, SITE_NAME } from '../../config/site';
import SiteLayout from '../../layouts/SiteLayout.astro';
---

<SiteLayout title={pageTitle('Terms & Conditions')} description="Terms and conditions for boat tours operated from Split.">
	<main id="main" class="content-page">
		<h1 class="content-page__title">Terms &amp; Conditions</h1>
		<p class="content-page__meta">
			Last updated: June 2026 · Draft for review — replace with counsel-approved wording before production.
		</p>

		<section class="sec">
			<h2 class="content-page__section-title">1. Operator</h2>
			<p class="content-page__paragraph">
				Services are offered by {SITE_NAME} and may be performed under entities referenced on your confirmation (e.g.
				Misericordia d.o.o., Aliskaf d.o.o., Per Mare d.o.o.) depending on vessel and season. The contracting party is
				stated on your booking confirmation.
			</p>
		</section>

		<section class="sec">
			<h2 class="content-page__section-title">2. Bookings &amp; preferred dates</h2>
			<p class="content-page__paragraph">
				The date you select expresses your preference. We confirm availability by email after payment or written
				acceptance. We do not guarantee a specific departure time until confirmed.
			</p>
		</section>

		<section class="sec">
			<h2 class="content-page__section-title">3. Itineraries &amp; weather</h2>
			<p class="content-page__paragraph">
				Routes, timings, and swim stops are indicative. The skipper may adjust or cancel stops for safety, harbour
				regulations, or sea conditions. Blue Cave and similar sites depend on operator rules and weather — entry may be
				unavailable without refund of separate ticket fees paid on-site.
			</p>
		</section>

		<section class="sec">
			<h2 class="content-page__section-title">4. Prices &amp; payments</h2>
			<p class="content-page__paragraph">
				Online payments are processed by PayPal. Quoted totals are calculated server-side before checkout. National park,
				cave, or similar entry fees may be payable separately unless explicitly included. Private charters are quoted on
				request.
			</p>
		</section>

		<section class="sec">
			<h2 class="content-page__section-title">5. Cancellation &amp; refunds</h2>
			<p class="content-page__paragraph">
				Cancellation terms depend on the product and notice period — publish your standard policy here before launch
				(e.g. free reschedule for weather cancellations by operator; customer cancellations X days before departure).
				Contact <a href={`mailto:${SITE_EMAIL}`}>{SITE_EMAIL}</a> for case-by-case requests.
			</p>
		</section>

		<section class="sec">
			<h2 class="content-page__section-title">6. Safety &amp; liability</h2>
			<p class="content-page__paragraph">
				Guests participate in marine activities at their own risk within the safety briefing provided. Minors must be
				supervised by a parent or guardian. Follow crew instructions at all times.
			</p>
		</section>

		<section class="sec">
			<h2 class="content-page__section-title">7. Governing law</h2>
			<p class="content-page__paragraph">
				These terms are governed by the laws of Croatia. Courts in Split have non-exclusive jurisdiction unless mandatory
				consumer law provides otherwise.
			</p>
		</section>
	</main>
</SiteLayout>

<style>
	.sec {
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}
</style>
